title: Michel Camilo chats about Dominican food and Culture; Intervista
description: Grammy® winning composer/pianist Michel Camilo has been living the American dream, born in the DR his life has been centered around music and food. Even after he’s lived in New York for thirty years he still has very delicious things to say about the cuisine of the Dominican Republic.
